week and the scope our annual the future now event profacts will be organising a webinar designed around the central theme the future mobility the last couple months profacts has conducted a serie studie and mystery shopping research involving citie and authorities the car industry the energy industry employers and citizens with the aim to uncover the attitude and behaviours the belgian population towards emobility our goal to get a clear view on the challenges facing the different stakeholder involved so will all cars be electric by it an illusion or can it become Reality that
